     H            Y.
     F** UTLR19 ********************************************
     F*  PROGRAM: GET MINUTE = TIME1 - TIME2               *
     F*  WRITTEN: JW (SRA)  2024.05.21                     *
     F*----------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UTLR19'
     F*                    PARM           $TM1    6
     F*                    PARM           $TM2    6
     F*                    PARM           $MIN    6
     F*                    PARM           $SIGN   1
     F*   IN  $TM1  :  6A FROM TIME (HHMMSS)
     F*   IN  $TM2  :  6A TO   TIME (HHMMSS)
     F*   OUT $MIN  :  6A MAX 999999
     F*   OUT $SIGN :  1A + OR -
     F******************************************************
     I            DS
     I                                        1   60WM1
     I                                        1   20WM1H
     I                                        3   40WM1M
     I                                        5   60WM1S
     I            DS
     I                                        1   60WM2
     I                                        1   20WM2H
     I                                        3   40WM2M
     I                                        5   60WM2S
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $TM1    6
     C                     PARM           $TM2    6
     C                     PARM           $MIN    6
     C                     PARM           $SIGN   1
      *--------------------------------------------------------
      *                    MAIN PROCESS
      *--------------------------------------------------------
      *
     C                     MOVEL$TM1      WM1
     C                     MOVEL$TM2      WM2
      * TM1
     C                     Z-ADDWM1S      WM1SS   60
     C           WM1M      MULT 60        NUM60   60
     C                     ADD  NUM60     WM1SS
     C           WM1H      MULT 3600      NUM60
     C                     ADD  NUM60     WM1SS
      * TM2
     C                     Z-ADDWM2S      WM2SS   60
     C           WM2M      MULT 60        NUM60   60
     C                     ADD  NUM60     WM2SS
     C           WM2H      MULT 3600      NUM60
     C                     ADD  NUM60     WM2SS
      *
     C           WM1SS     IFGE WM2SS
     C                     MOVE '+'       $SIGN
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE '-'       $SIGN
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           $SIGN     IFEQ '+'
     C           WM1SS     SUB  WM2SS     WM3SS   60
     C                     ELSE
     C           WM2SS     SUB  WM1SS     WM3SS
     C                     ENDIF
      * CONVERT TO MIN
     C           WM3SS     DIV  60        @MIN    60
     C                     MOVEL@MIN      $MIN
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
